29:59.993 --> 30:00.967
WHERE ARE YOU?
Don't worry about that.

30:00.967 --> 30:02.102
I DON'T WANT
TO TALK ABOUT IT

30:02.102 --> 30:02.936
NO MORE, BENJAMIN.

30:02.936 --> 30:04.237
ALL RIGHT, WELL, JUST ‐‐

30:04.237 --> 30:05.739
