AND HELP ME,

31:13.914 --> 31:15.215
AND WE'RE GONNA MAKE
THIS WORK.

31:15.215 --> 31:16.282
I FEEL LIKE WE CAN DO THIS.

31:16.282 --> 31:18.685
And I've been running
the numbers.

31:18.685 --> 31:21.187
