35:54.387 --> 35:55.889
OKAY, NO.
NO, I CAN'T. I CAN'T.

35:55.889 --> 35:56.923
I CAN'T DO THAT.
I CAN'T.

35:56.923 --> 35:57.991
JEFFERY.

35:57.991 --> 35:59.392
