38:55.288 --> 38:57.791
THANK YOU.

38:57.791 --> 39:00.594
WELL, NOW CAN I SPEAK?

39:00.594 --> 39:03.069
I WOULDN'T SPEAK FREELY,
BUT...

39:03.069 --> 39:04.805
[ SIGHS ]

39:04.805 --> 39:07.107
TRUST ME.
THIS WAS NECESSARY.

39:07.107 --> 39:10.844
WELL, WYATT HAS ALWAYS BEEN
OFF THE RAILS, EVER SINCE...

39:10.844 --> 39:12.112
THIS.

39:12.112 --> 39:13.680
IT WON'T WORK.

39:13.680 --> 39:16.382
THEY OFFERED HIM IMMUNITY
TO TESTIFY AGAINST US,

39:16.382 --> 39:17.618
AND HE TOOK THE DEAL.

39:17.618 --> 39:19.252
HE DID.

39:19.252 --> 39:21.387
IT WON'T WORK, KATHERYN.
NO?

39:21.387 --> 39:22.656
NO.

39:22.656 --> 39:23.857
HOW CAN YOU BE SO SURE?

39:23.857 --> 39:24.825
[ CHUCKLES ]

39:24.825 --> 39:27.293
I AM THE BEST.
MM.

39:27.293 --> 39:31.998
AND I'VE ALREADY STARTING
PLANNING M‐‐ OUR DEFENSE.

39:31.998 --> 39:34.000
BUT YOU HID THE CAR.

39:34.000 --> 39:35.035
NO, I DIDN'T.

39:35.035 --> 39:36.202
VERONICA?

39:36.202 --> 39:38.772
WHAT? NO, I DIDN'T.

39:40.140 --> 39:44.444
WHAT I DID, IS MY CLIENT,
WHO IS MY SON,

39:44.444 --> 39:46.279
TOLD ME WHERE THE CAR WAS.

39:46.279 --> 39:49.816
I WAS UNDER NO LEGAL OBLIGATION
TO TURN IT IN

39:49.816 --> 39:53.453
BECAUSE THAT WOULD HAVE
INCRIMINATED MY CLIENT.

39:53.453 --> 39:55.021
SO, JEFFERY
IS YOUR CLIENT, TOO?

39:55.021 --> 39:56.757
YES, AND SO ARE YOU.

39:56.757 --> 40:00.627
AND AS SOON AS WE CAN GET
A JUDGE ON THE PHONE,

40:00.627 --> 40:02.135
WE CAN GET US OUT OF HERE.
TRUST ME.

40:02.135 --> 40:03.537
[ SCOFFS ]
WHEN WILL THAT BE?

40:03.537 --> 40:04.805
I DON'T KNOW.

40:04.805 --> 40:07.741
THAT JENNIFER SALLISON
HAS IT IN FOR ME.

40:07.741 --> 40:09.676
YOU DID CALL HER
A DUMB BITCH.

40:09.676 --> 40:11.812
THERE'S MORE TO IT
THAN THAT.

40:11.812 --> 40:14.147
WHAT'S THE OTHER?

40:14.147 --> 40:16.216
THE WATERS RUN DEEP.

40:19.019 --> 40:21.755
AND SHE IS.

40:21.755 --> 40:23.857
HMM.

40:23.857 --> 40:26.426
WELL, TRY NOT TO SAY THAT
TILL THIS THING IS OVER.

40:26.426 --> 40:28.929
WELL, THAT'S GONNA BE VERY HARD,
BUT I WILL TRY.

40:28.929 --> 40:33.399
NOW...

40:33.399 --> 40:35.368
CAN WE TALK
ABOUT YOUR HAIR?

40:35.368 --> 40:37.504
NO, WE CANNOT.

40:37.504 --> 40:39.472
WHERE IS THAT GUARD?

40:39.472 --> 40:42.042
HEY,
WE NEED OUR PHONE CALL!

40:46.547 --> 40:48.114
[ WATER DRIPPING ]

40:50.517 --> 40:51.752
[ SIGHS ]

41:05.238 --> 41:07.173
OH, MY GOD,
THAT'S THE POLICE.

41:11.344 --> 41:12.913
RELAX. JEFFERY ‐‐

41:12.913 --> 41:14.948
LOOK, LOOK, LOOK, LOOK.
Shh. Shh. Shh.

41:14.948 --> 41:16.349
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

41:23.089 --> 41:25.058
WHAT SHOULD WE DO?

41:25.058 --> 41:26.126
[ POUNDING ON DOOR ]

41:27.728 --> 41:29.996
<i>NEXT ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

41:29.996 --> 41:31.532
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?!

41:31.532 --> 41:33.534
STOP! STOP!

41:33.534 --> 41:35.702
IS S‐SOMETHING WRONG?
UH, I'M SORRY.

41:35.702 --> 41:37.103
MA'AM, CAN YOU PUT SOME
CLOTHES ON, PLEASE?

41:37.103 --> 41:38.204
I HAVE TO FIND THE KEYS,

41:38.204 --> 41:39.506
AND I'M SURE THEY'RE
IN ONE OF HIS POCKETS.

41:39.506 --> 41:41.374
OH, GOD.

41:41.374 --> 41:42.943
JUSTIN,
WHERE'S THAT OTHER GUY?

41:42.943 --> 41:44.210
WHAT OTHER GUY?

41:44.210 --> 41:46.246
I SAW TWO GUYS OVER THERE.

41:46.246 --> 41:47.447
OH, JIM, PLEASE.

41:47.447 --> 41:48.915
IN THIS TOWN,
YOUR NAME IS LOWER

41:48.915 --> 41:50.884
THAN WHAT'S FLUSHED
IN THAT TOILET OVER THERE.

41:50.884 --> 41:53.720
IF I FIND OUT THAT ANYTHING
HAPPENED TO MY SON,

41:53.720 --> 41:56.757
THERE WILL BE NO POWER ON THIS
EARTH THAT WILL ESCAPE MY WRATH.
